{"tid":977492,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《刀劍神域》亞絲娜、《神曲奏界》克緹聲優戶松遙 宣布結婚消息","createTime":"2019-01-11T08:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T16:43:30.000Z","uid":43041,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d48495f8fc30968dbf47b2f1c12c72de82d210bf","tid":977492,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"過去曾飾演包含《刀劍神域》亞絲娜等&hellip;&hellip;多個角色，日本知名聲優 戶松遙，今（11）日於個人的官方 blog 上，宣布了結婚消息。<br />\n<br />\n　　戶松遙為日本知名聲優，曾飾演像是《神曲奏界》克緹、《刀劍神域》亞絲娜、《出包王女》菈菈、《我們仍未知道那天所看見的花名。》安城鳴子、《DARLING in the FRANXX》02 等&hellip;&hellip;眾多角色，至今在業界仍十分活躍。而她今日於個人的官方 blog 上公開了結婚消息，對象為一般男性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/11/163228_924c1191c4d7be7b2229cb8df6f110db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F11%2F163228_924c1191c4d7be7b2229cb8df6f110db.png&h=6a805916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　根據戶松遙表示，由於她很喜歡「1」這個數字，加上今天也是好日子的關係，因此就選在這個結合了 3 個她喜好數字的這一天結婚。雖然尚有許多不成熟的地方，但不論何時都會做自己，建築一個擁有開朗笑容的溫馨家庭。<br />\n <br />\n　　從 16 歲就開始從事聲優的戶松遙，不僅充實著過著每一天，也獲得了許多工作經驗及機緣。為此她也十分感謝，並表示今後在為人及演員上將會持續精進，並且對於從以前到現在一直支持著她的家人、朋友、工作夥伴、以及粉絲們抱持著感恩的心，持續在工作上努力。"},{"pid":"ae0816ddc9d4d79fb80f02a754740c8df0221025","tid":977492,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"咁桐人幾時結婚呀"},{"pid":"1354ad30e550a3f638f051025488bf3a93cfdf9f","tid":977492,"uid":476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"見到topic忽然間又想睇多次神曲奏界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618d9dd258deb2c85aca6a7b06e428c8b2961ac4","tid":977492,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"抄po 等收6c信"},{"pid":"4f16d7839913a28b68ac02e052b2b156cd6cbc7e","tid":977492,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"618d9dd258deb2c85aca6a7b06e428c8b2961ac4","tid":977492,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"抄po 等收6c信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:40:54.000Z","msg":"sor，無睇到有人出左<br />\n台主比次機會"},{"pid":"b5b0b7e9248aeae0f00d4f674865997d4237ac5d","tid":977492,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"咁係咪11月11結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86500e1d9ab3fdf88beaf74629f84e2477d7a83f","tid":977492,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"神曲奏界第2季明顯差週第1季<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dfc8ec5be779ab56312beefc7fd54215d40a33","tid":977492,"uid":135293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e993a81e35d8fe7b68f80adca4a6d9e324538ba","tid":977492,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16545b588f605ba828336399a38236413db4bd5f","tid":977492,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8c137256e01747a1515f70b75ac3e2294d77977","tid":977492,"uid":16870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1354ad30e550a3f638f051025488bf3a93cfdf9f","tid":977492,"uid":476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"見到topic忽然間又想睇多次神曲奏界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"黑提<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0868eb0f6719fc563a69d46106d1886269b1d43e","tid":977492,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb1afc3e15636e774cbc1710e46b2b1813b47554","tid":977492,"uid":